{
  "texts": [
    "Other papers on this topic continued to appear, e.g., [167] and [144].",
    "Relatedly, [21] have launched the problem of parameter reduction in N-soft sets.Distinctive positions have been taken for the study of this problem with fuzzy soft sets.",
    "Basu et al. [75] suggested a parameter reduction algorithm which is inspired by relational algebra.",
    "Also in this framework, [137] produced an adjustable approach to parameter reduction of fuzzy soft sets which is inspired by three-way decision.",
    "Kong et al. [148] studied normal parameter reduction from a new perspective."
  ]
}